    "description": "Kuehne+Nagel India invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Supply Chain Manager at our Bhubaneswar location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Kuehne+Nagel India:\nKuehne+Nagel India is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Implement warehouse management systems (WMS) and track KPIs\n• Handle customs clearance for import and export shipments\n• Manage a fleet of vehicles and coordinate with drivers\n• Implement cost-saving initiatives in transportation and warehousing\n• Manage reverse logistics and return merchandise authorization\n• Ensure compliance with transportation regulations and safety standards\n• Manage relationships with third-party logistics providers\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in GPS Tracking Systems\n• Proficiency in SAP SCM\n• Proficiency in Fleet Management\n• Proficiency in Reverse Logistics\n• Proficiency in Last Mile Delivery\n• Proficiency in KPI Monitoring\n• Proficiency in Freight Forwarding\n• Proficiency in INCOTERMS\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Meal coupons and food allowance\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Bhubaneswar, Odisha, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Kuehne+Nagel India!",
